column5: Out again Ths AM !!!  Another "FUN DAY"  Laker  IMG]http://i43.photobucket.com/albums/e389/KountryStar3910/IMG_1815_1.jpg[/img]  Couple of Whities  IMG]http://i43.photobucket.com/albums/e389/KountryStar3910/IMG_1816_1.jpg[/img]  A litle more Snow on the Way in!!!!   Got a Hot rear wheel on the Bike, Mabe a stuck,Frozen Brake Shoe  Gonna Hafta Take tomorrow off and do some equipment repairs.  Rick
nice going, you did much better then me  I couldn't find the people I was meeting up with so I just picked  a spot and fished I was skunked
put an opening bracket in front of the IMG so it looks like this  at the start so we can see the pics.

Good to see you got out there, Rick!  Jessy and I were out on Friday, but got nada!  We need to meet up again...it seems you were good luck for us    I can't see your pics, so I'm posting 'em in here...hope you don't mind...
Some nice whities & one VERY FAT laker !!!! well done... thanks for posting cheers

Thanks JB  I am not the sharpest Tool in the shed When it comes to 'Puters!!!  I have almost got the Reduce in size down and Now you want me to 'What' Any time you and LJ are up this way Let me Know!!  Rick

Hey Rick, another great day with your son I am sure...and with fish in the hut...hey who is complaining right?;-)) Noooooooooo-bodyyyyyyyy ;-))  I'll email you in case I can get away in the next week or so.  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
Great report and pics Rick Real nice looking Laker and whities.... congratulations and thanks for sharing Leechman

good stuff Rick  just got back from Nipissing--35 FOW  Vexilar gain 2--lots of Cisco-around the 11am-1pm witching hour-all the same size--only there mother can tell them apart  South Shore Ice Condos--40 below and more  Walleye were so so --mostly slot size decisions-no tropies--lol  no jurassic mud puppies--some jumbo perch--we fished hard  hope to you and your son on Simcoe this season  Tight lines all  ID1
Hey Terry is that not the norm for you lol. Needs some more lessons????? lol Ill show you in a few weeks how its done again lmao
